These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, blue, blood-red, mauve
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, hiking, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower, rose, zinnia
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, canasta, snooker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person who likes brown is between the person drinking fanta and the person playing bridge##2
 2. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is between the person driving the bus and the person playing snooker##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is the person who growsmarigold##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes blue##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Color          | blood-red | blue    | brown      | mauve  |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | writing    | camping       | hiking     |
| Flower   | rose        | zinnia       | sunflower          | marigold |
| Game           | canasta    | bridge | mah-jongg      | snooker     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

