 4. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who growstulip##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person playing go##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person playing domino is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who growssunflower is between the person driving the roller and the person who growsdahlia##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

